| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).event.id, round(vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).score,Int64(1))                                                             |
|               |   Sort: vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).event.id DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).score DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=10                                     |
|               |     Projection: vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).event.id, round(vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).score, Int64(1)), vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).score |
|               |       BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |         TableScan: vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")) projection=[event.id, score], full_filters=[vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).account.tier = Utf8("BUSINESS")]         |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[event.id@0 as event.id, round(vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).score,Int64(1))@1 as round(vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).score,Int64(1))]         |
|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [event.id@0 DESC, score@2 DESC], fetch=10                                                                                                                                    |
|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[event.id@0 DESC, score@2 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                        |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[event.id@0 as event.id, round(score@1, 1) as round(vector_search(delivery, Utf8("wrong location")).score,Int64(1)), score@1 as score]                                       |
|               |         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |           ProjectionExec: expr=[key@1 as event.id, 1 - distance@2 as score]                                                                                                                             |
|               |             BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |               FilterExec: account.tier@0 = BUSINESS                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                 CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                   RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                  |
|               |                     CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                       S3VectorsQueryExec: limit=30                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
